message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this great product to you first. I think it would really benefit you. What do you think about $200?
Hello Alice, thank you for the offer. I appreciate the value of the product, but I am looking to stay within my budget. Would you consider $180 for the product?
Hi Bob, I understand your budget concerns.  How about we meet in the middle at $190?
Hello Alice, I appreciate your willingness to negotiate. I am still looking to keep the cost below $190. Would you consider $185 for the product?
